    "content": "The Price Law Firm covers a full range of client needs in New York real estate practice, handling diverse matters from condo and co-op sales to rent control disputes. Founder Joshua C. Price has been concentrating on real estate law since 1997, offering a solid practical understanding of local markets and practices."
